metadata.name: BIR-CHI The Statue of Liberty
metadata.description:
The bird chose the Statue of Liberty to be included in the BIR-CHI treasure while visiting the United States of America.

The bird of the BIR-CHI Collection is the artist's soul, always seeking precious treasures. It may be her unfulfilled ambition to be a wanderer. 

The BIRd chooses a series of unique arCHItectural masterpieces to be preserved in the BIR-CHI treasures and the artist's mental pictures forever.
